"2019-08-11T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"認同，幫手推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警犬扮前線示威者</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光明正大勾結黑社會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">地鐵站內放催淚彈</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">布袋彈射爆示威者眼球</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">通街亂拉街坊同路人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">公安/武警冒充港警</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民譴責721</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac61cb6d852a2753532d05df9923c53c728366d2","tid":1446540,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"已經唔再需要和理非，全民勇武"},{"pid":"00b37164a59454dad22f2a627f1cb17107b47215","tid":1446540,"uid":83993,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ac61cb6d852a2753532d05df9923c53c728366d2","tid":1446540,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"已經唔再需要和理非，全民勇武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"罷買日同抵制濕鳩商戶係人人都可以做 同勇唔勇武係冇沖突"},{"pid":"6bdcbeddedfb7316c462e60a535b9be35eb7da34","tid":1446540,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7383d2d06acd5dd87fe9a63d1458d7315cee1325","tid":1446540,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a3adc9d42f19ffe627775d03155bc4d246da9d","tid":1446540,"uid":34063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:32:55.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5458bedfb17fa2f84ea827581c47a5903896cdf","tid":1446540,"uid":264124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b9c16479120ebab126058a87b4ea4c8beb217efe","tid":1446540,"uid":237219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c9648302bd46416b7b71221b37ed272606112257","tid":1446540,"uid":300851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd8a614e8d5fa3d8025ab856efeaedb198343c38","tid":1446540,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"武器制作"},{"pid":"6049470db7c760bc72f95d43fa2936238ba7bc36","tid":1446540,"uid":83993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d1a234910a77cbb4fe09a410843174919c1515","tid":1446540,"uid":280285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWapxCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWapxCD.jpg&h=b124281b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZP9JKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZP9JKj.jpg&h=687f6ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K0goOaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK0goOaZ.jpg&h=23ef5456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPz2jhF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPz2jhF.jpg&h=da80e324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RygDB4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?